strings.Value: "I'd so much like to discuss our day... but I'm… so… worn out…"
"I can barely keep my eyes open. I might just fall asleep where I stand!"
"That's a welcome change: finally some much needed quiet!"
"I could use some shut-eye too. But it's wrong to go sleep early. I don't want to get all softie!"
"The evening's quiet. Get some rest. Restore your strength."
"Starting tomorrow I'll carry half of your things. All right?
